OL,3,CMan pleads guilty after racially
OL,4,Cabusing and spitting at bus driver
OL,6,FA man who racially abused and spat at
OL,7,Fa bus driver in West London has been
OL,8,Fconvicted.
OL,10,FA video of the incident shows Michael
OL,11,FMongan, from Ealing, shouting at a bus
OL,12,Fdriver and spitting at him.
OL,14,FThe Metropolitan police said its
OL,15,Fofficers were called to Coldharbour
OL,16,FLane in Hayes at 12.25pm on Wednesday,
OL,17,F7th August. A video of the incident
OL,18,Fwas widely shared on social media.
OL,19,FOfficers then identified and arrested
OL,20,FMongan on Friday, 9th August.
