OL,3,CMan pleads guilty after racially
OL,4,Cabusing and spitting at bus driver
OL,6,FThe force said the bus driver had
OL,7,Frefused to let Mongan board as he did
OL,8,Fnot have enough money to pay for his
OL,9,Fjourney.
OL,11,FMongan then spat at the bus driver's
OL,12,Fcab a number of times while shouting
OL,13,FIslamophobic abuse and other threats.
OL,15,FOn Saturday, 10th August, he attended
OL,16,FUxbridge Magistrates' Court and
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty to a racially
OL,18,Faggravated public order offence, and
OL,19,Fanother charge of criminal damage.
