OL,3,CMan pleads guilty after racially
OL,4,Cabusing and spitting at bus driver
OL,6,FMongan remains in custody and is
OL,7,Fexpected to be sentenced at the same
OL,8,Fcourt on Tuesday, 13th August.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Jonathan Potter,
OL,11,Ffrom the Met Police, said:
OL,13,F"The bus driver who was racially abuse
OL,14,Fand spat at by Michael Mongan was
OL,15,Fsimply doing his job. He and all other
OL,16,Fstaff who work across London's
OL,17,Ftransport network have a right to do
OL,18,Fso in safety, free from unacceptable
OL,19,Fthreats and intimidation.
