OL,6,F"I hope the fast response from our
OL,7,Fofficers sends a clear message that we
OL,8,Fwill act to hold those who behave in
OL,9,Fthis way to account.
OL,11,F"I'm glad Mongan has been swiftly
OL,12,Fbrought to justice and will now face
OL,13,Fthe consequences of his actions."
